A data set for determining strata areas (hectares)

SA3_v2021.1.Rd

Data necessary for determining the amount of area a strata covers to expand estimates of biomass to be absolute. The SA3 data set was updated in March of 2021 to allow for splitting areas at the 40.16667, a common management line. The data includes the following columns:

  • OBJECT_ID

  • MIN_DEPTH_M

  • MAX_DEPTH_M

  • MIN_LAT_DD

  • MAX_LAT_DD

  • AREA_HECTARES

  • INPFC_AREA

Usage

SA3_v2021.1

Format

A data frame.
